      "html": "<style data-kid=\"0\">\n  @import url('https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=satoshi@700,900&display=swap');\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');\n\n  :root {\n    --color-indigo-900: #312e81;\n    --color-amber-500: #f59e0b;\n    --color-border: #e2e8f0;\n  }\n\n  body {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    color: var(--color-indigo-900);\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n\n  .font-satoshi {\n    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .editorial-row {\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n    padding-top: 3rem;\n    padding-bottom: 3rem;\n  }\n\n  .selection-amber::selection {\n    background: var(--color-amber-500);\n    color: white;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"min-h-screen selection-amber\" data-kid=\"1\">\n  \n  <nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-100\" data-kid=\"2\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 h-20 flex items-center justify-between\" data-kid=\"3\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"4\">\n        <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-[#312e81] flex items-center justify-center font-satoshi font-bold text-white rounded-none\" data-kid=\"5\">R</div>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-xl tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"6\">Register</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-10\" data-kid=\"7\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider\" data-kid=\"8\">Expertise</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider\" data-kid=\"9\">Portfolio</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider\" data-kid=\"10\">Méthode</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#312e81] text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"11\">\n          Consultation\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n\n  \n  <header class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pt-24 pb-32\" data-kid=\"12\">\n    <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start\" data-kid=\"13\">\n      <div class=\"lg:col-span-8\" data-kid=\"14\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-6xl md:text-8xl font-satoshi font-black leading-[0.95] tracking-tighter mb-10\" data-kid=\"15\">\n          ARCHITECTURE <br data-kid=\"16\">\n          DIGITALE SUR <br data-kid=\"17\">\n          <span class=\"text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"18\">MESURE</span>\n        </h1>\n        <p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 font-normal max-w-[60ch] leading-relaxed mb-12\" data-kid=\"19\">\n          L&apos;agence Register conçoit des infrastructures numériques de haute précision. Nous transformons la complexité technique en autorité commerciale.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center max-w-lg\" data-kid=\"20\">\n          <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Votre adresse professionnelle\" class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 border border-slate-300 focus:border-indigo-900 outline-hidden font-medium\" data-kid=\"21\">\n          <button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto whitespace-nowrap px-10 py-4 bg-indigo-900 text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"22\">\n            Analyser mon site\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"lg:col-span-4 border-l border-slate-100 pl-8 space-y-12\" data-kid=\"23\">\n        <div data-kid=\"24\">\n          <span class=\"block text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"25\">+47.2%</span>\n          <span class=\"block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold mt-1\" data-kid=\"26\">Croissance organique moyenne</span>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"27\">\n          <span class=\"block text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"28\">-18.4h</span>\n          <span class=\"block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold mt-1\" data-kid=\"29\">Économie opérationnelle / semaine</span>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"30\">\n          <span class=\"block text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"31\">0.74s</span>\n          <span class=\"block text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold mt-1\" data-kid=\"32\">Temps de chargement critique</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"border-y border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50\" data-kid=\"33\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-10\" data-kid=\"34\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center opacity-40 grayscale gap-12\" data-kid=\"35\">\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"36\">Dubosc & Fils</span>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"37\">Lemaire Artisan</span>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"38\">Boulangerie Dupont</span>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"39\">Trans-Val Group</span>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"40\">Morel Engineering</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <main class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-24\" data-kid=\"41\">\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"editorial-row grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12\" data-kid=\"42\">\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-4\" data-kid=\"43\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-amber-600 mb-4\" data-kid=\"44\">I. Méthodologie</h2>\n        <h3 class=\"text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold leading-tight\" data-kid=\"45\">Notre Approche</h3>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-8 space-y-10\" data-kid=\"46\">\n        <div class=\"group border-b border-slate-50 pb-8\" data-kid=\"47\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"48\">\n            <span class=\"text-slate-200 font-satoshi group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"49\">01</span>\n            Analyse Structurelle\n          </h4>\n          <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl pl-10\" data-kid=\"50\">\n            Audit complet de votre écosystème digital pour identifier les goulots d&apos;étranglement et les opportunités de croissance non exploitées.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"group border-b border-slate-50 pb-8\" data-kid=\"51\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"52\">\n            <span class=\"text-slate-200 font-satoshi group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"53\">02</span>\n            Ingénierie Évolutive\n          </h4>\n          <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl pl-10\" data-kid=\"54\">\n            Développement d&apos;une base technique robuste utilisant Next.js et des architectures headless pour garantir performance et scalabilité.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"group\" data-kid=\"55\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"56\">\n            <span class=\"text-slate-200 font-satoshi group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"57\">03</span>\n            Maintenance Prédictive\n          </h4>\n          <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl pl-10\" data-kid=\"58\">\n            Support continu et optimisation des Core Web Vitals pour maintenir votre position de leader sur votre marché local.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"editorial-row grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mt-12\" data-kid=\"59\">\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-4\" data-kid=\"60\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-amber-600 mb-4\" data-kid=\"61\">II. Réalisations</h2>\n        <h3 class=\"text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold leading-tight\" data-kid=\"62\">Études de Cas</h3>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-8\" data-kid=\"63\">\n        <div class=\"bg-indigo-900 text-white p-12 relative overflow-hidden group\" data-kid=\"64\">\n          <div class=\"relative z-10\" data-kid=\"65\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-400 mb-2 block\" data-kid=\"66\">Maison Lemaire — Ébénisterie de Luxe</span>\n            <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-satoshi font-bold mb-6\" data-kid=\"67\">Restaurer l&apos;autorité numérique d&apos;un artisan</h4>\n            <div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-sm opacity-80 mb-10\" data-kid=\"68\">\n              <div data-kid=\"69\">\n                <span class=\"block font-bold mb-1 uppercase tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"70\">Défi</span>\n                <p data-kid=\"71\">Site obsolète, 0 visibilité sur les requêtes locales stratégiques.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"72\">\n                <span class=\"block font-bold mb-1 uppercase tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"73\">Impact</span>\n                <p data-kid=\"74\">+68.4% de demandes de devis qualifiées en 90 jours.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:gap-5 transition-all\" data-kid=\"75\">\n              Consulter l&apos;analyse <i class=\"lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" data-kid=\"76\"></i>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 w-80 h-80 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-amber-500/10 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"77\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"editorial-row grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mt-12\" data-kid=\"78\">\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-4\" data-kid=\"79\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-amber-600 mb-4\" data-kid=\"80\">III. Investissement</h2>\n        <h3 class=\"text-4xl font-satoshi font-bold leading-tight\" data-kid=\"81\">Structure Tarifaire</h3>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md:col-span-8\" data-kid=\"82\">\n        <div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-slate-200 border border-slate-200\" data-kid=\"83\">\n          <div class=\"bg-white p-10\" data-kid=\"84\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-2\" data-kid=\"85\">Essentiel Architectural</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8\" data-kid=\"86\">Idéal pour établir une présence digitale indiscutable.</p>\n            <span class=\"text-3xl font-satoshi font-bold block mb-8\" data-kid=\"87\">SUR DEVIS</span>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-10\" data-kid=\"88\">\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"89\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"90\"></i> Design sur-mesure</li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"91\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"92\"></i> SEO Local Optimisé</li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"93\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"94\"></i> Hébergement Haute-Disponibilité</li>\n            </ul>\n            <button class=\"w-full py-4 border border-indigo-900 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-indigo-900 hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"95\">\n              Demander une Estimation\n            </button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"bg-slate-50 p-10 relative\" data-kid=\"96\">\n            <div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 bg-amber-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"97\">Prioritaire</div>\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-2\" data-kid=\"98\">Advanced Systems</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8\" data-kid=\"99\">Pour les infrastructures complexes et applications métiers.</p>\n            <span class=\"text-3xl font-satoshi font-bold block mb-8\" data-kid=\"100\">SUR DEVIS</span>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-600 mb-10\" data-kid=\"101\">\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"102\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"103\"></i> Architecture Headless</li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"104\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"105\"></i> Intégrations API / CRM</li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"106\"><i class=\"lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-amber-500\" data-kid=\"107\"></i> Dashboard d&apos;Administration</li>\n            </ul>\n            <button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-indigo-900 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"108\">\n              Réserver un Audit\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </main>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-indigo-900 py-32 text-center px-8\" data-kid=\"109\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"110\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-satoshi font-black text-white leading-tight mb-8\" data-kid=\"111\">\n        VOTRE TRAJECTOIRE DIGITALE <br data-kid=\"112\">\n        COMMENCE ICI.\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"text-lg text-indigo-200 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"113\">\n        Nous ne construisons pas seulement des sites. Nous bâtissons des actifs numériques qui travaillent pour vous 24h/24.\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"114\">\n        <button class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-white text-indigo-900 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"115\">\n          Request Architectural Review\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"px-12 py-5 border border-white text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\" data-kid=\"116\">\n          Consulter l&apos;Archive\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"bg-white border-t border-slate-100 py-16 px-8\" data-kid=\"117\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8\" data-kid=\"118\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"119\">\n        <div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center font-satoshi font-bold text-white text-[10px]\" data-kid=\"120\">R</div>\n        <span class=\"font-satoshi font-bold text-lg tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"121\">Register</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex gap-10 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400\" data-kid=\"122\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"123\">Mentions Légales</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"124\">Confidentialité</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-indigo-900\" data-kid=\"125\">Cookies</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300\" data-kid=\"126\">\n        © 2026 Register Agency. Built for impact.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>\n\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\" data-kid=\"127\"></script>\n<script data-kid=\"128\">\n  lucide.createIcons();\n</script>",
